UTOPIA
======

UTOPIA is a student productivity app built for college students. It consolidates
multiple academic tools — notes, attendance tracking, AI assistance, real-time
chat, campus mapping, and gamification — into a single offline-first mobile app.

Website: https://inferalis.space

Quick Start
-----------

* Report a bug: Open an issue on GitHub
* Get the latest version: https://github.com/infernoGurala/utopia-app/releases
* Build the app: See Getting Started section below
* Join the community: https://inferalis.space

Essential Documentation
-----------------------

All users should be familiar with:

* Features: See Features section below
* Architecture: See Architecture section below
* Design System: See Design System section below
* Tech Stack: See Tech Stack section below

Documentation can be found in the README or viewed online at:
https://inferalis.space


Who Are You?
============

Find your role below:

* Student - Using UTOPIA for academics and campus life
* Class Rep / Writer - Managing content and communicating with students
* Developer - Contributing to the UTOPIA codebase
* Academic Researcher - Studying app architecture and design


For Specific Users
==================

Student
-------

Welcome! UTOPIA has everything you need for college:

* Library: Browse community notes and files with full offline access
* Luna: Get AI-powered academic help, attendance-aware responses
* Attendance: Track your college portal attendance securely
* Chat: Message friends with custom emojis
* SciWordle: Daily science word game with streaks and leaderboards
* Campus Map: Find friends on campus (8AM-10PM IST)
* Notifications: Receive morning schedule updates and broadcasts
* Search: Find any note content instantly

Class Rep / Writer
------------------

Manage content and communicate with students:

* Developer Panel: Access writer tools from Profile > Developer Mode
* Timetable Editor: Update weekly class schedule from the app
* Notes Management: Edit notes in the utopia-content repository
* Quotes Editor: Manage the morning quote pool
* Broadcast: Send urgent messages to all students instantly
* Folder Visibility: Hide/show library folders from readers
* Manual Notifications: Trigger morning notifications manually

Developer
---------

Contribute to the UTOPIA codebase:

* Getting Started: See Getting Started section below
* Architecture: lib/services/ contains all business logic
* Firebase Setup: Configure Auth, Firestore, and Cloud Messaging
* GitHub Actions: Morning notifications and broadcasts automation
* Content Storage: Separate utopia-content repo for notes and files
* Build Commands: flutter build apk --release for Android
* Code Style: Follow Flutter/Dart conventions

Academic Researcher
-------------------

Explore UTOPIA's architecture and design:

* Architecture: Service layer pattern with screens never touching Firebase
* Offline-First: SQLite caching with auto-sync on app open
* Multi-Provider AI: Configurable failover across Groq, Gemini, OpenAI
* Real-Time Systems: Firestore for chat, Realtime DB for location
* Free Infrastructure: Entire stack runs on free tiers (Firebase, GitHub Actions)
* Security: AES-128-CBC encryption for credentials, flutter_secure_storage
* Design System: Material 3 with Catppuccin colour palette


Features
========

Library — Notes & Files
-----------------------

* Community notes with Markdown rendering and LaTeX math support
* File attachments (PDFs, slides) from Google Drive, cached for offline
* Full-text search across all cached content via SQLite
* Note segment sharing — tap any heading or paragraph to share it
* Hidden folders support for writers

Luna — Intelligent Academic Assistant
------------------------------------

* Multi-provider AI with automatic failover (Groq, Gemini, OpenAI-compatible)
* Context-aware responses using timetable, attendance, and available notes
* Attendance-aware answers to "can I skip class?"
* Conversation history with last 20 messages
* Clean markdown responses with structured formatting

Attendance
---------

* Direct scraping from info.aec.edu.in college portal
* AES-128-CBC encrypted credential storage
* Subject-wise breakdown with progress bars
* 75% threshold tracking per subject

Chat & Friends
-------------

* Real-time 1-on-1 messaging via Firestore
* 120+ custom kawaii emoji system across 7 categories
* Typing indicators and online/offline presence
* Message actions — reply, edit, unsend
* Note sharing directly into conversations

Campus Map
----------

* Google Maps locked to Aditya University campus
* Real-time friend location sharing (8AM-10PM IST only)
* Catppuccin-themed dark map style
* Per-user location sharing toggle

SciWordle — Daily Science Word Game
-----------------------------------

* Daily science-themed Wordle with variable word length
* Scoring system with streak bonuses
* Anti-cheat — results locked after playing
* Leaderboard ranked by total score
* Champion badges for top players (Legend, GOAT)

Morning Notifications
---------------------

* Daily schedule at 5:00 AM IST
* Luna-style format: Morning/Afternoon schedule, Must Carry, Quote
* Fully automated via GitHub Actions
* Holiday detection with custom messages

Timetable
---------

* Weekly class schedule with day tabs
* Writers can edit via visual UI in-app
* Data stored as JSON in content repository

In-App Updates
--------------

* Version checking via Firestore
* Optional and forced update support
* Direct APK download with progress indicator
* Native Android package installer


Architecture
============

Service Layer
------------

All business logic lives in lib/services/ — screens never touch Firebase
or HTTP directly.

* AIService — Multi-provider AI chat with failover and history
* AttendanceService — Portal scraping, AES encryption, HTML parsing
* GitHubService — Content sync, folder/file listing, note caching
* WriterGitHubService — Write-back to GitHub (timetable, quotes, folders)
* CacheService — SQLite database for folders, files, notes, settings
* FileCacheService — Binary file downloads and local caching
* ChatService — Real-time messaging, typing state, unread counts
* ChatEmojiCatalog — 120+ custom emoji definitions with inline rendering
* NotificationService — FCM, local notifications, background handling
* BroadcastService — Writer broadcast via GitHub Actions
* SciwordleService — Daily game state, scoring, streaks, leaderboard
* GameChampionService — Real-time top-3 rankings
* RoleService — Writer role checking with caching
* LocationService — GPS for campus map
* AppUpdateService — Version checking, APK download, install
* SecureStorageService — Encrypted credential storage
* SearchService — Full-text search across cached notes

Screen Layer
-----------

* HomeScreen — Library browser with folders, files, sync
* NoteViewerScreen — Markdown rendering with segment sharing
* AttendanceScreen — Login, subject breakdown, progress bars
* UniversityScreen — Friends, Community, Events, Everyone tabs
* FriendsScreen — User list with presence and champion badges
* ChatScreen — 1-on-1 messaging with emoji picker
* IaaScreen — Luna AI assistant chat interface
* MapScreen — Campus map with live location sharing
* SciwordleScreen — Daily word game UI
* SciwordleLeaderboard — Score rankings with champions
* SciwordleStatsScreen — Personal game statistics
* ProfileScreen — Settings, theme, developer mode access
* DeveloperPanelScreen — Writer tools hub
* TimetableScreen — Weekly schedule viewer
* TimetableEditorScreen — Visual editor for writers
* BroadcastScreen — Urgent message sender

Navigation
----------

AppShell (BottomNavigationBar)
├── Library (HomeScreen)
├── Attendance (AttendanceScreen)
├── University (UniversityScreen → FriendsScreen, etc.)
└── Profile (ProfileScreen)

Secondary screens pushed via Navigator.push: Note Viewer, IAA, Chat,
Map, SciWordle, Developer Panel, Search, etc.


Design System
=============

UTOPIA uses Catppuccin Mocha colour palette with Material 3 components
and Outfit as the primary typeface.

* Background: #1E1E2E (Base)
* Surface: #313244 (Surface0)
* Primary: #CBA6F7 (Mauve)
* Text: #CDD6F4 (Text)
* Subtext: #A6ADC8 (Subtext0)
* Accent: #94E2D5 (Teal)
* Green: #A6E3A1
* Yellow: #F9E2AF
* Error: #F38BA8 (Red)
* Border: #45475A (Surface1)

Theme system supports multiple named palettes with flexible tokens.


Tech Stack
==========

* App framework: Flutter 3.41.5 (Dart 3.11.3)
* Auth: Firebase Auth (Google Sign-In)
* Database: Cloud Firestore + Firebase Realtime Database
* Local cache: SQLite (sqflite) + path_provider
* Push notifications: Firebase Cloud Messaging + flutter_local_notifications
* Content storage: GitHub (utopia-content repo)
* File storage: Google Drive (shared folder)
* Automation: GitHub Actions (notifications, broadcasts)
* AI providers: Groq, Gemini, OpenAI-compatible
* Maps: Google Maps SDK
* Attendance: Direct scraping with AES-128-CBC encryption
* Markdown: flutter_markdown + flutter_math_fork (LaTeX)
* Security: flutter_secure_storage, encrypt package
* Design: Material 3 + Catppuccin Mocha
* Typography: Google Fonts (Outfit)

Monthly cost: 0 — entire stack runs on free tiers.


